import React from 'react';
import { StyleSheet,View,Text,ScrollView } from 'react-native';
import { Appbar,Card, Button,Title,Paragraph  } from 'react-native-paper';

function Products() {
    return (
         <ScrollView style = {styles.background}>
           <Text style={styles.st}>Deals</Text>  
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/camera.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/socket.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/keyfinder.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View>
           <Text style = {styles.boxText}>  See More</Text>
           <Text style={styles.st}>Recomendation</Text>  
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/inverter.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/bluetooth.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/homeauto.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View>
           <Text style={styles.st}>Electric</Text>  
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/switch.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/socket.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/inverter.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View>
           <Text style={styles.st}>Lighting</Text>  
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/camera.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/socket.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/keyfinder.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View>
           <Text style={styles.st}>Security</Text> 
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/camera.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/socket.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/keyfinder.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View> 
           <Text style={styles.st}>Motor Controls</Text>  
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/camera.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/socket.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/keyfinder.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View>
           <Text style={styles.st}>Curtin Opener</Text>  
           <View style = {styles.productBox}>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/camera.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/socket.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           <Card style = {styles.card}>
               <Card.Cover source={require('../assets/keyfinder.png')} style = {styles.cardCover}/>
           </Card>
           </View>
         </ScrollView>
    );
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
     background: {
          backgroundColor: '#EEEEEE',
         
     },
     card: {
          width: '30%',
          height: 100,          
      },
     cardCover: {
          width: '100%',
          height: '100%'
     },
     productBox: {
          alignItems: "center",
          flexDirection: "row",
          justifyContent: "space-around",
          marginTop: 10
     },

     // btn: {
     //      backgroundColor: '#242945',
          
      
     // },
     st:{
          color:'#242945',
          fontSize:15,
          borderBottomWidth: 2,
          width:'31%',
          fontWeight:"bold",
          marginLeft: 10,
          marginTop:'2%'
     },
     boxText: {
          margin:10,
          width:'20%',
          backgroundColor: '#d4aa04',
          color: "lightGrey",
          fontWeight: "Bold",
          marginLeft:'75%'
     }
     // st2:{
     //      color:'#242945',
     //      fontSize:16,
     //      fontWeight:"bold",
     //      fontStyle:"italic"
     // }
}

);

export default Products;
